trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectListCommand" /> objects.

trans-unit.source: The class object provides the container for the commands of an <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList>.
trans-unit.target: O objeto da classe fornece o contêiner para os comandos de um <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList>.

trans-unit.source: Accessing the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList.Commands%2A> property of an <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList> retrieves an <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectListCommandCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Acessando o <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList.Commands%2A> propriedade de um <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList> recupera um <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectListCommandCollection> objeto.

trans-unit.source: An application can programmatically add or remove commands.
trans-unit.target: Um aplicativo pode adicionar programaticamente ou remova os comandos.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectListCommandCollection> class implements the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> interface through the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ArrayListCollectionBase> class.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectListCommandCollection> classe implementa o <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> por meio da interface de <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ArrayListCollectionBase> classe.

trans-unit.source: For a complete example, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList> overview.
trans-unit.target: Para obter um exemplo completo, consulte o <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.ObjectList> visão geral.
